text: An image shared on Facebook allegedly shows the stage that will be used for President-elect Joe Biden’s inauguration ceremony being built in front of the White House.
Photo shows Biden’s inaugural stage being built on the White House North Lawn.
An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows President Joe Biden on a movie set meant to look like the White House.
A picture of U.S. President Joe Biden in front of the White House in March 2022 was staged or digitally altered to add trees.
